nt chunks to FileStore.\n        3. Splits parent chunks into child chunks.\n        4. Injects parent_id into child", "metadata": {"source": "plugins/vector-db/skills/vector-db-agent/scripts/operations.py", "type": "py", "last_modified": 1771739109.5424135}}